A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Baltimore County – Speed Monitoring Systems – Funding for Traffic Calming
3 Devices
4 FOR the purpose of requiring the governing body of Baltimore County to establish, by law,
5 a special fund that may be used only to assist in covering certain costs of traffic
6 calming devices on county roads; requiring the fines collected by Baltimore County
7 as a result of violations enforced by the speed monitoring systems to be deposited in
8 the special fund; and generally relating to the use of fines collected by Baltimore
9 County as a result of violations enforced by speed monitoring systems.
